sleuth-responsible for adding the trace id and span id to http headers.
Zipkin- aggregating those traces and display on dash board.

Add these dependencies in all project- api gateway,productservice and coupon service

       <dependency>
			<groupId>org.springframework.cloud</groupId>
			<artifactId>spring-cloud-starter-sleuth</artifactId>
		</dependency>
		
		<dependency>
			<groupId>org.springframework.cloud</groupId>
			<artifactId>spring-cloud-sleuth-zipkin</artifactId>
		</dependency>
		
		
	Now All service are registered with Eureka server-product sercice,coupon service and api gateway	
		
now install zipkin server in machine which runs at port 9411		
to test-  http://localhost:9411/zipkin/  (Zipkin Dash board).

